title: Jerry vs. Zeke, Texans-Seahawks Trade, Aaron Rodgers and The Herd Hierarchy
itunes:title: Jerry vs. Zeke, Texans-Seahawks Trade, Aaron Rodgers and The Herd Hierarchy
description:
Colin details the PR battle between Jerry Jones and Ezekiel Elliott, his thoughts on the Houston Texans-Seattle Seahawks trade, Aaron Rodgers getting his way, and his Herd Hierarchy. Guests include Doug Gottlieb, Reggie Bush, Solomon Wilcots, and Hue Jackson.
